        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">Squarespace AI</h3>
          <span class="bg-[#7C3AED] text-white px-6 py-3 font-black text-xl">9.0/10</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-6 font-bold">Beautiful studio templates with audio samples, equipment galleries, and booking forms.</p>
