            <p class="font-black text-green-700 mb-3">✓ PROS</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Stunning studio templates (portfolio-quality layouts)</li>
              <li>• Audio players built-in (SoundCloud, Spotify embeds)</li>
              <li>• Equipment galleries (gear photos with specs)</li>
              <li>• Email capture (artist list building)</li>
              <li>• Booking form integration (Calendly, Acuity)</li>
              <li>• Mobile-optimized (79% musicians browse mobile)</li>
              <li>• $23-59/month (reasonable for studio portfolio)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-red-700 mb-3">✗ CONS</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Template limits (customization constrained)</li>
              <li>• Limited customization (can't build unique layouts)</li>
              <li>• Monthly commitment (can't pause during slow months)</li>
              <li>• No booking system native (requires Calendly add)</li>
              <li>• Equipment gallery basic (no CMS organization)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
