        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wix -->
      <div class="mb-12 border-[3px] border-purple-400 p-8 bg-purple-50">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900">Wix AI</h3>
          <span class="bg-purple-500 text-white px-6 py-3 font-black text-xl">8.6/10</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-6 font-bold">Music studio templates with booking systems and package pricing.</p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-green-700 mb-3">✓ PROS</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Booking features built-in (Wix Bookings native)</li>
              <li>• Package pricing (hourly/daily rates easily set)</li>
              <li>• Easy setup (5-minute AI generation)</li>
              <li>• Mobile app (manage bookings on-the-go)</li>
              <li>• Audio embeds (SoundCloud one-click)</li>
              <li>• Template variety (more studio options)</li>
              <li>• $17-46/month (cheapest for booking features)</li>
