          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-green-700 mb-3">✓ PROS</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li>• Custom design (unique studio brand expression)</li>
              <li>• Equipment CMS (organize gear by category/room)</li>
              <li>• Fast PageSpeed (95+ Core Web Vitals)</li>
              <li>• Export capability (move to hosting if needed)</li>
              <li>• Client testimonials CMS (organize reviews easily)</li>
              <li>• Animation polish (micro-interactions impress)</li>
